  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial package declares assuranceLevel Medium while multiple credibility factors show achievedLevel below requiredLevel, triggering COMPOUND-03 (assurance-level overstatement). Decision is recorded as Accepted despite critical gaps, embedding W-AR-02.",
