    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model provides Medium assurance for the VAD COU. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is considered a compensating measure for identified factor gaps. The model is accepted as the primary basis for hemolysis submission to the regulatory authority. Remaining gaps in model form, output comparison, and test samples are noted for post-market surveillance follow-up.",
